statements: SELECT * FROM SwimmingEventRankings ORDER BY event_id DESC;
SELECT event_name, swimmer_name, swim_time FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE ranking > 3;
SELECT swimmer_name, event_name, swim_time, ranking FROM SwimmingEventRankings ORDER BY swim_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE swimmer_name = 'Michael Phelps';
SELECT event_name, swimmer_name, swim_time, ranking FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE event_name LIKE '%Freestyle%' ORDER BY ranking ASC;
SELECT * FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE event_id = 1 ORDER BY swim_time DESC, ranking ASC
SELECT event_name, swim_time, ranking FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE swim_time < '00:30:00' AND ranking > 3 ORDER BY ranking DESC
SELECT event_name, swimmer_name, swim_time FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE event_name LIKE '%breaststroke%' ORDER BY event_name ASC
SELECT * FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE swim_time BETWEEN '00:25:00' AND '00:27:00' ORDER BY swim_time ASC, ranking ASC
SELECT swimmer_name, swim_time, ranking FROM SwimmingEventRankings WHERE swim_time > '00:28:00' AND ranking <= 5 ORDER BY swimmer_name DESC, ranking ASC
SELECT * FROM SwimmingEvents;
SELECT EventName, EventDate FROM SwimmingEvents WHERE EventDate > '2022-01-01';
SELECT EventName, Rank FROM SwimmingEvents INNER JOIN EventRankings ON SwimmingEvents.EventID = EventRankings.EventID;
SELECT * FROM EventRankings WHERE Rank <= 3 ORDER BY Rank DESC;
SELECT EventName, EventDate, Rank FROM SwimmingEvents LEFT JOIN EventRankings ON SwimmingEvents.EventID = EventRankings.EventID;
SELECT EventName, EventDate FROM SwimmingEvents WHERE EventDate >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM SwimmingEvents WHERE EventName LIKE '%freestyle%';
SELECT EventName, Rank FROM SwimmingEvents JOIN EventRankings ON SwimmingEvents.EventID = EventRankings.EventID WHERE Rank <= 3 ORDER BY Rank DESC;
SELECT EventName, COUNT(SwimmerID) AS TotalSwimmers FROM SwimmingEvents JOIN EventRankings ON SwimmingEvents.EventID = EventRankings.EventID GROUP BY EventName;
SELECT EventName, EventDate FROM SwimmingEvents ORDER BY EventDate ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM EventRankings;
SELECT event_name, athlete_name, country FROM EventRankings;
SELECT athlete_name, ranking FROM EventRankings ORDER BY ranking DESC;
SELECT event_name, country FROM EventRankings WHERE event_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM Standings WHERE total_points > 100 ORDER BY total_points DESC;
SELECT event_id, event_name, ranking, athlete_name, country FROM EventRankings WHERE country = 'USA' ORDER BY event_id DESC;
SELECT athlete_name, country, total_points FROM Standings WHERE total_points > 100 ORDER BY total_points DESC, athlete_name ASC;
SELECT event_id, event_name, update_text, update_time FROM EventRankings JOIN Updates ON EventRankings.event_id = Updates.event_id WHERE event_id = 1 ORDER BY update_time DESC;
SELECT event_id, event_name, athlete_name, country FROM EventRankings WHERE ranking BETWEEN 1 AND 3 ORDER BY event_id, ranking DESC;
SELECT standing_id, athlete_name, country, total_points FROM Standings WHERE country = 'Canada' AND total_points < 50 ORDER BY total_points ASC, athlete_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM Event;
SELECT Event_Name, Event_Date FROM Event WHERE Event_ID = 1;
SELECT Participant_Name, Participant_Country FROM Participant WHERE Participant_ID IN (1, 2, 3);

SELECT Event.Event_Name, Participant.Participant_Name, Ranking.Event_Rank FROM Event INNER JOIN Ranking ON Event.Event_ID = Ranking.Event_ID INNER JOIN Participant ON Ranking.Participant_ID = Participant.Participant_ID;

SELECT Event_Event_ID, Event_Name, Participant_Name, Standings_Position FROM Standings LEFT JOIN Event ON Standings.Event_ID = Event.Event_ID LEFT JOIN Participant ON Standings.Participant_ID = Participant.Participant_ID ORDER BY Standings_Position DESC;
SELECT * FROM Event WHERE Event_Date = '2022-10-15';
SELECT Participant_Name, Participant_Country FROM Participant ORDER BY Participant_Name DESC;
SELECT Event_Name, Event_Date FROM Event WHERE Event_Date > '2022-01-01' AND Event_Date < '2022-12-31';

SELECT Event.Event_Name, Participant.Participant_Name, Ranking.Event_Rank FROM Event JOIN Ranking ON Event.Event_ID = Ranking.Event_ID JOIN Participant ON Ranking.Participant_ID = Participant.Participant_ID;
SELECT Standings_Position, Standings_Time FROM Standings WHERE Event_ID = 1 ORDER BY Standings_Position ASC, Standings_Time DESC;
SELECT * FROM event;
SELECT event_name, event_location, event_date FROM event ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT swimmer_name, swimmer_country, swimmer_birthdate FROM swimmer WHERE swimmer_country = 'USA';
SELECT team_name, team_country FROM team WHERE team_country = 'Canada';
SELECT swimmer_name, event_name, time FROM swimmer INNER JOIN competition ON swimmer.swimmer_id = competition.swimmer_id INNER JOIN event ON competition.event_id = event.event_id ORDER BY time ASC;
SELECT * FROM event WHERE event_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT event_name, event_date FROM event ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT swimmer_name, swimmer_country FROM swimmer WHERE swimmer_country = 'USA';
SELECT event_name, event_location FROM event WHERE event_location LIKE '%pool%';
SELECT team_name, team_country FROM team WHERE team_country != 'Canada';
